<h2 class="bold font-l">Kirby 64: Bad Ending</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
If you beat the boss of Ripple Star without collecting every crystal shard, you'll be treated to an ending that seems happy, until... </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LastNoteNightmare" class='trope-example-link'>Last Note Nightmare</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
